Each user can also check the status of three other users.
If a potential risk is detected, the app not only recommends self-isolation, but also sends a notification to local health authorities. Analyzing big data collected from mobile phones, facial recognition technology, mobile phone tracking and artificial intelligence – such tools are used to track infected people and people they have contacted in South Korea, Taiwan and Singapore.
